headline: Bernstein Lifts Lockheed Martin Corporation (LMT)’s Price Target, Citing Strong Top-line Growth Outlook
summary: Lockheed Martin Corporation (NYSE:LMT) is among the 10 Largest Defense Stocks in 2025. On October 20, Bernstein lifted the stock’s price target to $545 from $497 and maintained a Market Perform rating. The adjustment came a day ahead of the company’s Q3 2025 earnings call and represented an upside potential of 8% from Monday’s close. […]
